      <title>经济部长说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-05/softbank-s-arm-inks-landmark-chip-deal-with-malaysia-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SoftBank-backed chipmaker Arm Holdings Plc has agreed to license chip designs and technology to Malaysia over the next decade, as the nation eyes semiconductor exports of 1.2 trillion ringgit ($270 billion) by 2030. Malaysian Economy Minister Rafizi Ramli speaks exclusively to Bloomberg Television&#39;s Haslinda Amin about the details of the pact as the nation targets manufacturing its own chips within五到七年。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
