      <title>随着美国希望削减成本，中国加大了在军队上的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-ramps-up-spending-on-its-military-as-us-looks-to-cut-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将在2025年将其国防支出提高约7.2％，与去年的增长相匹配，并反映了习近平总统的野心，他们建立了可以挑战美国的军队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-ramps-up-spending-on-its-military-as-us-looks-to-cut-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 00:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将官方预算赤字提高到30多年来最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-boosts-official-budget-deficit-to-highest-in-over-30-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将其一般预算赤字提高到了三十多年来的最高水平，因为北京增加了支出以应对美国关税上升的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-boosts-official-budget-deficit-to-highest-in-over-30-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 00:09:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管美国关税，中国将GDP目标设定为约5％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-sets-gdp-target-at-about-5-despite-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将其经济增长目标设定为2025年的5％，这提高了人们对与美国贸易战面对更多刺激的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-sets-gdp-target-at-about-5-despite-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 00:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税释放的迹象火花不确定性时，石油延长了下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）表示，特朗普政府可以退缩墨西哥和加拿大的一些关税，向全球市场注入更多的不确定性，因此石油降低了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 23:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
